OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start with
OL,6,Fsunny spells, the best of these across
OL,7,Feastern parts with cloud increasing in
OL,8,Fthe west. Scattered showers will
OL,9,Fdevelop for the afternoon.
OL,10,FOccasionally fresh southwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny showers soon dying out
OL,13,Fthen some late sunny spells. Remaining
OL,14,Fdry overnight with long clear spells.
OL,15,FWinds becoming light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
