OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA bright start with sunny
OL,6,Fspells but cloud increasing through
OL,7,Fthe morning with outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fedging east, although the eastern
OL,9,FBorders remains dry and bright until
OL,10,Flate afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy,
OL,13,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing
OL,14,Fthen sunny spells and showers Sunday.
OL,15,FSunny spells and just a few showers
OL,16,FMonday, but cloudier Tuesday with
OL,17,Foccasionally heavy rain or thundery
OL,18,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
